NAME
	summoning - a method to summon a demon

DESCRIPTION
	If a lesser thief is in dire need of high-level assistance,
	they can request a demon to arrive to help them. A demon is
	a very high level and skilled thief.

	Just chant the demon's name three times and he (she) might
	come to help you.

	E.g.	'cant daedalus daedalus daedalus'

	You got to be in a place that allows teleportation, of course.
	Demon is not forced to obey.

SEE ALSO
	demon
